import numpy as np

def algorithm(train_samples, train_parity, test_samples):
    n = train_samples.shape[1]
    aug_matrix = np.hstack((train_samples, train_parity[:, np.newaxis]))
    for i in range(n):
        pivot_row = np.argmax(aug_matrix[i:, i]) + i
        aug_matrix[[i, pivot_row]] = aug_matrix[[pivot_row, i]]
        if aug_matrix[i, i] == 1:
            mask = aug_matrix[i+1:, i] == 1
            aug_matrix[i+1:][mask] ^= aug_matrix[i]
    true_bits = np.zeros(n, dtype=int)
    for i in reversed(range(n)):
        true_bits[i] = aug_matrix[i, n] ^ np.sum(aug_matrix[i, i+1:n] & true_bits[i+1:])
    test_parity = np.sum(true_bits & test_samples, axis=1) & 1
    return test_parity
